title: What happened to August 'jinxylord' Browning is he making champions anymore
body:
Today I decided to see who created my favorite/main champion Ekko. seeing that it is Jinxlord and the other champions he created I am stunned that he has not made one since Ekko. I mean Jinx, Ekko, Gnar, and Vi are probably my top 10 favorite champions and Jhin is also pretty good. I mean he also created Rengar but I can let that slide for these others. Is he designing more champions or what I would really like to know.


EDIT 1: Ok I see he created Kai Sa, but it wasnt credited to him on his wiki page so SORRY. still Ekko - Kai Sa was a very large gap.
